'''Hyderabad Metropolitan Water Supply and Sewerage Board''' (HMWSSB) was established on 1 November 1989, in [[Hyderabad, India]]. It looks for the supply of water to the household and sewerage services of the city.<ref name=H>http://www.hyderabadwater.gov.in/wwo/UI/about_us.aspx</ref> 

HMWSSB was formed by the [[Andhra Pradesh Government]] with the provisions of Hyderabad Metropolitan Water Supply and Sewerage Act 1989 (Act No.15 of 1989).<ref name=H />

